#: ../../S/SO.rst:10
msgid ""
"(also S.O.) Abbrev. for Significant Other, almost invariably written "
"abbreviated and pronounced /S·O/ by hackers. Used to refer to one's primary "
"relationship, esp. a live-in to whom one is not married. See :ref:`MOTAS`\\,"
" :ref:`MOTOS`\\, :ref:`MOTSS`\\."
msgstr ""
"(S.O.とも) Significant "
"Other(重要な他者)の略。ハッカーはほぼ必ず略して書き、/S·O/と発音する。自分の主要な関係、とくに結婚していない同棲相手を指して使う。\\ "
":ref:`MOTAS`\\ 、\\ :ref:`MOTOS`\\ 、\\ :ref:`MOTSS`\\ を参照。"

